==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ilium
<hw>Il"i*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Ileum</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>The dorsal one of the
three principal bones comprising either lateral half of the pelvis; the
dorsal or upper part of the hip bone. See <cref>Innominate bone</cref>,
under <er>Innominate</er>.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>ilion</asp>,
and <asp>ileum</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ilixanthin</ent>⟦br⟧
